{"word":"G879 - ἀφυπνόω - aphypnóō - af-oop-no'-o - Fall asleep","slug":"G879","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀφυπνόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>aphypnóō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>af-oop-no'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Fall asleep"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C6;&#x03C5;&#x03C0;&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - aphupnoo&#x0304;</b> - <i>af-oop-no'-o</i><p/>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G5258\">G5258</a>; properly to <i>become awake</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>drop</i> (off) in slumber: - fall asleep."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1797\">G1797</a>, <a href=\"#/G1798\">G1798</a>, <a href=\"#/G1852\">G1852</a>, <a href=\"#/G1853\">G1853</a>, <a href=\"#/G5258\">G5258</a>"}]}